Class Node

java.lang.Object
api.Node
All Implemented Interfaces:
node_data
Direct Known Subclasses:
DWGraph_Algo.Node_Algo
public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements node_data
This class represents the set of operations applicable on a node (vertex) in a directed weighted graph.
Author:
Shaked Aviad & Rotem Halbreich
